I doubt any server is really TG friendly per say but I like to think that
on this mailing list we are all TG friendly =)

Rodcet is a nice place to go because lots of people are there, and I'm a
guide there =D

Brell Serilis seems like a nice server too, my enchanter Luna married her
sweetheart Duna and no one has been mean about it though some people have
been confused. My Ranger Pixy is also dating a female paladin Aeani and
again no real problems. Brell also has a fair number of people from the
list on it.

You could go anywhere, but these servers give you a good start for queer
positive people!

Tina
